          "content": "<div class=\"accordion space-y-4\" id=\"faq-accordion\">\n  <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: $TEXT_PRIMARY$; margin-bottom: 32px;\">\n    Terms of use for digital service items\n  </h2>\n\n  <!-- Accordion Item 1 -->\n  <div class=\"accordion-item font-normal\" style=\"margin-top: 4px;\">\n    <button\n      class=\"accordion-toggle w-full flex items-center justify-between text-left font-semibold\"\n      style=\"padding: 12px 0; background: transparent; border: none; cursor: pointer; color: $TEXT_PRIMARY$;\"\n    >\n      <span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\">When do the months start to run during which I can use the service in a position without additional payment?</span>\n      <svg\n        class=\"accordion-icon transition-transform duration-300 rotate-180\"\n        fill=\"none\"\n        stroke=\"currentColor\"\n        stroke-width=\"2\"\n        viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\n        style=\"width: 18px; height: 18px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-left: 16px;\"\n      >\n        <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\" />\n      </svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"accordion-content\" style=\"padding: 8px 16px 16px; background: transparent; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: $TEXT_SECONDARY$;\">\n      From the date of signing the contract of your subscription plan.\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; margin: 4px 0;\" />\n\n  <!-- Accordion Item 2 -->\n  <div class=\"accordion-item font-normal\" style=\"margin-top: 4px;\">\n    <button\n      class=\"accordion-toggle w-full flex items-center justify-between text-left\"\n      style=\"padding: 12px 0; background: transparent; border: none; cursor: pointer; color: $TEXT_PRIMARY$;\"\n    >\n      <span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\">Do I have to pay extra for the services?</span>\n      <svg\n        class=\"accordion-icon transition-transform duration-300\"\n        fill=\"none\"\n        stroke=\"currentColor\"\n        stroke-width=\"2\"\n        viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\n        style=\"width: 18px; height: 18px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-left: 16px;\"\n      >\n        <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\" />\n      </svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"accordion-content hidden\" style=\"padding: 8px 16px 16px; background: transparent; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: $TEXT_SECONDARY$;\">\n      Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry.\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; margin: 4px 0;\" />\n\n  <!-- Accordion Item 3 -->\n  <div class=\"accordion-item font-normal\" style=\"margin-top: 4px;\">\n    <button\n      class=\"accordion-toggle w-full flex items-center justify-between text-left\"\n      style=\"padding: 12px 0; background: transparent; border: none; cursor: pointer; color: $TEXT_PRIMARY$;\"\n    >\n      <span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\">How do I manage my digital services positions?</span>\n      <svg\n        class=\"accordion-icon transition-transform duration-300\"\n        fill=\"none\"\n        stroke=\"currentColor\"\n        stroke-width=\"2\"\n        viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\n        style=\"width: 18px; height: 18px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-left: 16px;\"\n      >\n        <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\" />\n      </svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"accordion-content hidden\" style=\"padding: 8px 16px 16px; background: transparent; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: $TEXT_SECONDARY$;\">\n      Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry.\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; margin: 4px 0;\" />\n\n  <!-- Accordion Item 4 -->\n  <div class=\"accordion-item font-normal\" style=\"margin-top: 4px;\">\n    <button\n      class=\"accordion-toggle w-full flex items-center justify-between text-left\"\n      style=\"padding: 12px 0; background: transparent; border: none; cursor: pointer; color: $TEXT_PRIMARY$;\"\n    >\n      <span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\">I can&#39;t fill my digital services position</span>\n      <svg\n        class=\"accordion-icon transition-transform duration-300\"\n        fill=\"none\"\n        stroke=\"currentColor\"\n        stroke-width=\"2\"\n        viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\n        style=\"width: 18px; height: 18px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-left: 16px;\"\n      >\n        <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\" />\n      </svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"accordion-content hidden\" style=\"padding: 8px 16px 16px; background: transparent; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: $TEXT_SECONDARY$;\">\n      Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry.\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; margin: 4px 0;\" />\n</div>",
